---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="首頁"
  description="太平洋鸚鵡（Pacific Parrotlet）完整飼養指南 — 幼鳥挑選、手養方式、親人訓練、健康檢查、日常照護"
  currentPath="/"
  pageImage="/images/parrot-wild.jpg"
  pageImageAlt="野生太平洋鸚鵡（Pacific Parrotlet）"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">🦜 完整飼養指南</div>
    <h1>太平洋鸚鵡飼養指南</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Pacific Parrotlet Care Guide — <em>Forpus coelestis</em></p>
    <p class="hero-desc">全世界最小的鸚鵡之一，卻有著大鳥的個性。本指南涵蓋從幼鳥挑選到日常照護的所有知識，幫助您與口袋鸚鵡共度 15–25 年的美好時光。</p>
  </section>

  <div class="quick-info card">
    <h2>🔍 物種速覽</h2>
    <table>
      <tr><th>學名</th><td>Forpus coelestis</td></tr>
      <tr><th>別名</th><td>太平洋鸚哥、Celestial Parrotlet、口袋鸚鵡</td></tr>
      <tr><th>原生地</th><td>厄瓜多西部、祕魯西北部（太平洋沿岸）</td></tr>
      <tr><th>體型</th><td>10–12 公分（全世界最小鸚鵡之一）</td></tr>
      <tr><th>體重</th><td>31–34 公克</td></tr>
      <tr><th>壽命</th><td>人工飼養 15–25 年</td></tr>
      <tr><th>性格</th><td>膽大、好奇、有主見、領地性強</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2>📖 飼養指南總覽</h2>
  <div class="card-grid">
    <a href="/selecting-chicks" class="card-link">
      <div class="card glass-card">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-icon">🥚</div>
        <h3>幼鳥挑選</h3>
        <p>最佳年齡、健康檢查表、性別判斷、向繁殖者提問清單。</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/hand-feeding" class="card-link">
      <div class="card glass-card">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-icon">🍼</div>
        <h3>手養方式</h3>
        <p>成長時程表、配方調配、餵食步驟、保溫需求、斷奶流程。</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/taming" class="card-link">
      <div class="card glass-card">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>親人訓練</h3>
        <p>適應期、建立信任、上手訓練、棍棒訓練、正向強化。</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/health-check" class="card-link">
      <div class="card glass-card">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-icon">🏥</div>
        <h3>健康檢查</h3>
        <p>每日檢查、疾病徵兆對照表、血羽處理、卡蛋急救、醫院籠設置。</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/daily-care" class="card-link">
      <div class="card glass-card">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-icon">🏠</div>
        <h3>日常飼養</h3>
        <p>飲食比例、籠具環境、家中危險源、睡眠、洗澡。</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/behavior" class="card-link">
      <div class="card glass-card">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>行為特質</h3>
        <p>單隻 vs 一對飼養建議、與其他寵物相處、飼養提醒。</p>
        <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero Section ── */
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    background: rgba(0,212,255,0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.20);
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* ── Quick Info Card ── */
  .quick-info {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .quick-info h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Glass Card Grid ── */
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card-link {
    text-decoration: none !important;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    perspective: 800px;
  }

  .glass-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100%;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* Accent gradient bar on top of each card */
  .card-accent {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg) var(--radius-lg) 0 0;
  }

  .card-link:hover .card-accent {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-link:hover .glass-card {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.25);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .glass-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .glass-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .card-arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--cyan-dim);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s;
  }

  .card-link:hover .card-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 2rem 0.5rem 1.5rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .card-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
